She woke up and stepped out of the CR chamber.  She felt much better now.  
She needed that repair and recharge. She stood there for a second and saw 
that her commlink light was blinking.  She pushed the button and it replayed 
Archangle's last message about the VOK technology.

"Oh uh.  Why do I have the feeling that this mean trouble?"
